              <p class="d-none d-sm-block mb-0 p-2">日本産科婦人科学会に集積されている不妊治療実施施設の成績の開示を求める署名活動にご協力ください！</p>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="mb-3">
                  <%= link_to image_tag("info/signing_activity.png", class: "img-fluid pb-1", loading: "lazy"), "https://www.change.org/p/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%A3%E7%A7%91%E5%A9%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E4%BC%9A-%E9%81%A9%E5%88%87%E3%81%AA%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%8A%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E6%96%BD%E8%A8%AD%E3%82%92%E9%81%B8%E6%8A%9E%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%81%9F%E3%82%81%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%A3%E7%A7%91%E5%A9%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E4%BC%9A%E3%81%AB%E9%9B%86%E7%A9%8D%E3%81%95%E3%82%8C%E3%81%9F%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE%E3%83%87%E3%83%BC%E3%82%BF%E3%81%AE%E9%96%8B%E7%A4%BA%E3%82%92%E6%B1%82%E3%82%81%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99?recruiter=47187004&utm_source=share_petition&utm_medium=twitter&utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_initial&utm_term=psf_combo_share_initial&recruited_by_id=debe3cf0-851d-0130-2ac1-00221968d0e0", target: '_blank', rel: "nofollow" %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <p class="d-block d-sm-none small mb-0 p-2">はじめて体外受精･顕微授精を行う方（初採卵後１ヵ月以内の方）、以下アンケート調査にご協力ください！</p>
              <p class="d-none d-sm-block mb-0 p-2">はじめて体外受精･顕微授精を行う方（初採卵後１ヵ月以内の方）、以下アンケート調査にご協力ください！</p>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <%= link_to image_tag("info/saitamaika.png", class: "img-fluid pb-1", loading: "lazy"), "http://www.saitama-med.ac.jp/hospital/division/33gynecology/predictionivf.html", target: '_blank', rel: "nofollow" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <p class="d-block d-sm-none small mb-0 p-2">体外・顕微授精で妊娠/出産された方へ。ぜひレポコの投稿をお願いします！</p>
              <p class="d-none d-sm-block mb-0 p-2">体外・顕微授精で妊娠/出産された方へ。ぜひレポコの投稿をお願いします！</p>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="mb-3">
                  <%= link_to image_tag("info/lets_repoco.png", class: "img-fluid pb-1", loading: "lazy"), signup_path %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-5">
          <div class="rounded-lg">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p>＼ <span class="marker-underline"><i>最新レポコを配信中</i></span> ／</p>
              <p class="small">レポコをはじめ、不妊不育治療情報をお届けします<%= image_tag"home/finger_mom_down.svg", width: "20px", class: "m-0 p-0", loading: "lazy" %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2 popup_area">
                <%= link_to "https://twitter.com/repoco_official", {class: "text-decoration-none w-100", target: :_blank, rel: "noopener noreferrer"} do %>
                  <button class="tw_blue_btn"><%= image_tag"action/Twitter_Social_Icon_Rounded_Square_Color.svg", width: "35px", class: "img-fluid", loading: "lazy" %>@REPOCO_OFFICIALをフォロー</button>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block pl-2 pr-0">
      <%= render 'right' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>